Package: genepair
Type: Package
Title: Functions to Analyse Pairs of Genomic Elements like Genes.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Jonas", "Ibn-Salem", email = "j.ibn-salem@uni-mainz.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides several functions to analyse pairs of 
    genomic elements. For exmaple the function applytoClosePairs can calculate 
    efficiently correlation of gene expression across many gene pairs that are
    within a certain distance on the same chromosome.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.2)
Imports:
    GenomicRanges (>= 1.24.3),
    plyr (>= 1.8.4),
    BiocParallel (>= 1.8.1),
    data.table (>= 1.10.4),
    GenomeInfoDb (>= 1.10.3)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: testthat
